article_text:
Oneonta, NY (13820)

Today

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms during the afternoon. High 83F. Winds SW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening, with mostly cloudy skies after midnight. Low 62F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 40%.

article_metadata.author: Denise Richardson Staff Writer

og.description: April 15 has passed but Monday's deadline for filing tax returns hovers.
og.title: Tax experts tackle busy week
